

**Mamtsh ab toꞌi g Jesus g uhw shuhdagikaj **

*An g neid g Matthew 26:6-13; Mark 14:3-9 *

1 Chuhdp tash o wa am wiꞌis mat wo e ai g t‑shohshon ha‑doꞌibiadag wuhshda. 2 Kud wa am hab e juh g geꞌe gegosig Bethany t am wehhejed g Jesus. Kuchd gam hu hihim k am ha wehm t‑gegosid. D g Lazarus am ep t‑wehmaj. Marda ad am ha wehmaj hegam mad am hihidod ch an t‑toꞌid. 3 D g Mary ged hu jiwia Jesus wui k g si s‑namkig uhw shuhdagi uꞌa ch an iawua Jesus tahtad an. K eda d hemako s‑wehch. D an i dagio wabsh g e‑cheꞌechew moꞌokaj. D wehsko uhwa ihda uhw shuhdagi am kih ch ed. 

4 D hab kaij hegai t‑wehm kehshaj g Jesus mo hab chehgig Judas Iscariot, 5 “T haschu ahgk pi e gagda ihda uhw shuhdagi matt wo ha mah g shoꞌigkam, natt pi ahim g waik siant pihsh namkigdag ab wo i nei g lial heg amjed.” 6 D eda pi woho s‑ha hoꞌigeꞌid g shoꞌigkam ch wabshaba s‑behimk g lial nadki pi s‑chu ehsk ch chum nuhkud g t‑lialiga ch wabsh hejel hekaj. 

7 D hab kaij g Jesus ab wui, “Dagitoni. T‑himdag oidk at hab juh g ni‑muhkig wehhejed. 8 Chum o hekid ia em‑shahgid g shoꞌigkam. Nt wabshaba ahni hi pi wabsh chum hekid ia wo em‑shahgidk.” 

**Mamsh g Lazarus hab waꞌap chum s‑muꞌamk **

9 D eda wehsko kaidag mad g Jesus ab i wuhshad g Lazarus muhkig amjed. Kud muꞌi am dada g Judea t am hemajkam s‑ha neidamk. 10-11 Kud muꞌijj ab i s‑wohoch mo g Jesus d Jiosh si Kehsha k am i ha dagito g e‑wanimeddam am i neidok g Lazarus. D am i s‑mai g uꞌugchu papal k am i e nako mat g Lazarus hab waꞌap wo mua. 

**Mash muꞌijj si s‑hehgig ch ahg mo g Jesus d Jiosh si Kehsha **

*An g neid g Matthew 21:1-11; Mark 11:1-11; Luke 19:28-40 *

12 D am baꞌich i mahsi. Kuchd am i t‑nakog k gam hu hihi Jerusalem wui. D eda muꞌi am e hemapadch g hemajkam kihhim ch ed mat wo wuhshad g t‑shohshon ha‑doꞌibiadag. Chd am hihim wohg ch ed. D muꞌijj ga hu t‑nam am i kaiok mat am wo jiwia g Jesus. 13 Idam ad ha uhꞌukch g chukud shosha uꞌus iꞌibhonig ch ab si has elid g Jesus si s‑kaidam hab kaijch, “Id o d s‑apꞌekam t‑kownalig ch ia jiwia am wehhejed g Jiosh. K g Jiosh si s‑hoꞌigeꞌid.” 

14 D g Jesus am hema ha tai g wechij wuhlu k heg cheshadk. 

15 Heki o hu an hab chuꞌig Jiosh oꞌohana ed matsh id hab wo e juh ch hab chuꞌig: 

Pi g am wo e totodsid, ahpim Tutuligo\! 

Idani at ia wo jiwia g geꞌe em‑kownalig an daichugch wechij wuhlu t an. *Zechariah 9:9 * 

16 Kuchd pi shaꞌi amichud wehs ihda. Kut wa wabshaba hekid ab uhgk i e bei g Jesus dahm kahchim wui, tt am hahawa i chegito mo an oꞌohanas ihda Jiosh oꞌohana ed. Kutki heg hekaj hab e juh am wehhejed. 

17-18 Idam muꞌi hemajkam ad wa am nam g Jesus nash pi kah mat ab i wuhshad g Lazarus muhkig amjed. Hegam mo wa am neid ash am ha ahgid. 19 D hab kaij g Palasi ab aꞌai e wui am i ha neidok, “Ha g wo neid matki wehsijj am i oi. Pi attki wo t‑nako matt wo keshwua.” 

**Mash haꞌi g Greek oꞌodham s‑neidamk g Jesus **

20 D am haꞌi dada g Greek hemajkam Jerusalem t am mat ab wo has el g Jiosh heg eda doꞌibiadag wuhshda piast. 21 Kuchd am oiopo. D idam am dada k am cheh g Philip k am ahgi mo s‑neidamk g Jesus. 22 D g Philip am ahgi g Andrew. \(Idam ad am d chum kihkam Bethsaida t am am Galilee chekshani ch ed.\) Kud am hahawa e wehm hihim k am ahgi g Jesus. 

23 D hab kaij g Jesus ab ha wui, “Idani at e ai g ni‑tashga mat g ni‑ohg wo ni‑maskogi mani d si Kehshaj. 24 T wabshaba wehpeg haꞌichu hab wo e juh am ni‑tahgio. Neh, nat hig am wo i wuhshani k ab wo muꞌida g pilkani pi am hu e eshk? Hemho wa at am wo e ei jewed wecho k wo muh k hab waꞌi masma wo i wuhshani k ab wo muꞌida. 25 Id ani hab ahg mat g oꞌodham wo heki wua g e‑doakag matp wo s‑huwidad hejel e wehhejed k wabshaba wo edgidad g pi ha huhugedam doakag matp wo hugio g e‑doakag am ni‑wehhejed. 26 Bat wo junihid g ni‑tatchui hegai matp hedai hab e elid mat d wo ni‑pionagk. Kunt hab wo juh mat an wo ni‑wehmajk mant hebai wo i haꞌichugk. Ni‑ohg at ab wo si has i ha el hegam mo hab junihim g ni‑tatchui.” 

**Mash g Jesus am ahg g e‑muhkig **

27 D hab ep kaij g Jesus, “Ni‑ihbdag at ab si i e kudu. Ni hab chum ni‑tahtk mant hab wo chei, ‘Ni‑ohg, pi g hiwgid mas hab wo e juh ihda am ni‑tahgio.’ Nt eda heg hekaj ia jiwia mant am wo gahi wuhsh hegai s‑koꞌok haꞌichu. 28 Pegih, ni‑ohg, am g maskogid g e‑gewkdag am gahi ni‑wuhshanim.” 

D ab neo g Jiosh dahm kahchim t amjed k hab kaij, “Am ant heki hu i maskogid k am hab ep wo juh.” 

29 Muꞌi o wa am gegok g hemajkam ch kah hegai mo ab neok. Haꞌijj o hab kaij, “Ab o kaidaghim g tataniki.” 

Kud haꞌijj hab kaij, “Anghil at ab wui neo.” 

30 D Wabshaba hab kaij g Jesus ab ha wui, “Ahpim at em‑wehhejed ab s‑kaidam neo, ch pi ahni ni‑wehhejed. 31 E at ai mat geꞌe wo bei g chuꞌijig g hemajkam. Jijawul ha‑geꞌejig o chum e kownalchud id dahm jewed. Nt wabshaba oi wo gewito. 32 Ab amt wo ni‑naggia uhs t ab ahni Jiosh si Kehsha. Kunt ab haha wo i ha wanchshul g hemajkam ni‑wui.” 33 Neh, bo wa kaij g Jesus ch oki heg hab ahg mat has masma wo muh. 

34 D hab kaij g hemajkam, “An o hab chuꞌig Jiosh oꞌohana ed mat g Jiosh si Kehsha pi hekid wo muh. P haschu ahgch hab kaij mapt ab wo e naggia uhs t ab maptp woho d Jiosh si Kehsha?” 

35 D hab kaij g Jesus ab ha wui, “Ia ant heꞌes i tash wo haꞌichugk em‑shahgid ch heg wa wepo mani d tonlig em‑wehhejed. Am g s‑ap wo hihimad tonlig oidch. T hab pi wo em‑maꞌish g s‑chuhugam. Hegai matp hedai am wo himad s‑chuhugam k ed o pi mahch mas hebai him. 36 Ab g wo i s‑ni‑wohochud mani eda ia wabsh kia haꞌichug k hab masma tonlig ch ed wo hihimad.” Neh, bad kaij ch gam hu hahawa i e mehkod ab ha amjed. 

**Matsh muꞌijj g Tutuligo pi ab hu i wohoch g Jesus **

37 Muꞌikko ad wa hab juh g s‑hasig haꞌichu g Jesus am ha‑nena ed idam hemajkam. Kud wabshaba muꞌijj pi ab hu wohochud mo d Jiosh si Kehsha. 38 Neh, d hab wa masma hab e juh hegai matki g kelibad Jiosh haꞌichu i tashogiddam Isaiah an oꞌoha. An o hab chuꞌig: 

Pi o muꞌi ab s‑wohochud g haꞌichu t‑ahga ab m‑amjed. 

K g m‑gewkdag pi tasho am ha‑wehhejed. *Isaiah 53:1 * 

39-41 Tki an ep oꞌoha g Isaiabad: 

Jiosh at hab ha juh mo pi ap haꞌichu neid ch pi haꞌichu amichud mat pi ab hu wui wo i e nohnogid k pi wo e doꞌibia ab pi apꞌekam t amjed. *Isaiah 6:9-10 * 

Isaiabad o wa ab amjed neok g Jesus gewkdag natsh pi Jiosh am tashogi. Kut idam hemajkam wa woho pi e nako mas ab wo s‑wohoch g Jesus. 

42 Kud muꞌi ab hi wa chum s‑wohoch g hahaꞌichu. Tsh wabshaba g Palasi gam hu wo i ha wuwhas matp wo s‑mai mat ab s‑wohoch. D heg hekaj pi am hu tasho e ahg 43 no pi s‑hohhoꞌid g ab has ha‑elida g hemajkam ch g Jiosh ab has elida wabsh pi ab hu haꞌichuchud. 

**Mamt wabsh wo e lodai g Jesus neꞌokikaj **

44 Jesus ad am ep ha jehnigid ch si s‑kaidam hab kaij, “Matp hedai ab wo i s‑ni‑wohochud k hab waꞌap s‑wohochud g ni‑ohg Jiosh. 45 K hedai i ni‑neid ch hab waꞌap neid. 46 Ia ant jiwia id dahm jewed k hab sha masma mo g tonlig am em‑wehhejed nani pi am tashogid g wohokam himdag. Kumt s‑ap wo himad g e‑doakag hab masma mam am tonlig ch ed mamtp ab wo ni‑hiwgad. 47 Muꞌijj o pi ab hu ni‑kaiham ch pi ab hu ni‑hiwig. Nt wabshaba pi heg hekaj ia jiwia manis wo ha lodai. S‑ha ani doꞌibiamk. 48 T wo e lodai g ni‑neꞌokikaj mat hekid wo i huhug g jewed. 49 Ni‑ohg o ab ni‑chehani mant haschu hab wo chei. Ni pi g hejel ni‑neꞌoki hab kaij. 50 Kumt heg hekaj ab wo kaiham k hab wo bei g pi ha huhugedam doakag. Heg ani waꞌi hab kaij mo g Jiosh ab ni‑chehani.” Neh, bad kaij g Jesus. 

